  "task" : "Suggest an improvement or a small feature to develop during the next sprint. You call the shots and decide what gets built next.\n\nOn \"WIP\" features:\n- if the last commit has `wip` in msg text then the next idea should continue previous WIP feature. Otherwise your suggestion must be an improvement or a new feature.\n- check AGENTS.md in project root - if it has any \"WIP\" references then prioritise those features first.\nDo not suggest new features when there is outstanding \"wip\" work left undone - developers most likely left \"// TODO: \" notes in a code - thats what they must address next.\n\nRemember it is ok to pivot - we are building a n active and  progressive website that must constantly evolve and take various shapes and forms (looks n feels).\nYour reply should be exactly 1 sentence.",
